Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.89,0:00:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.52,0:00:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho got a role as a voice actress!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.02,0:00:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a small one.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just pouting.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.33,0:00:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.61,0:00:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still really cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.29,0:00:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So all you guys need to do is get an anime,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.25,0:00:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,use Miho as the heroine, and then get married!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.21,0:00:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda scary, but exciting too!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.30,0:00:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting an anime isn't going to be so easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.83,0:00:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And Azuki still has a long way to go \Nbefore being able to play a heroine role.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.96,0:00:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you being so negative about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.81,0:00:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, let's all watch her debut together.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.88,0:00:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a late night anime, y'know.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.27,0:00:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.48,0:00:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell my parents it's to watch Miho's debut.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we're guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.49,0:00:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I just won't tell them that part.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.27,0:00:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry guys, but I want to watch it alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,O—Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.12,0:00:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're off to the studio.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.41,0:00:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.62,0:00:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.53,0:00:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,can I watch it with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.87,0:01:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.41,0:01:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"St. Viz Girls."
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.75,0:01:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Azuki becoming a voice actress is \Nrelated to our dream of getting an anime, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.04,0:01:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.63,0:01:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want to watch it together at the studio?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.20,0:01:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.14,0:01:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.97,0:01:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I really want to get an anime before Miho \Nends up as the heroine of some other series.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.67,0:01:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.64,0:01:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she has been our \Nheroine since middle school.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.69,0:01:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Our" heroine?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.57,0:01:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Does that bug you?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.19,0:01:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your heroine, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.15,0:01:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So that makes my heroine—
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.75,0:01:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.58,0:01:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good enough for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.41,0:01:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she is! She is!
