Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A heroine—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One everybody will love.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.08,0:03:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.04,0:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.54,0:03:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,After drawing the realistic style for "The \NTwo Earths" and "Money and Intelligence,"
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.26,0:03:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't draw any cute girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not use that one?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.34,0:03:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The drawing of Azuki you \Nmade last year in your notebook.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,N—No good?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't realistic.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.23,0:03:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was really cute, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.39,0:03:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that a lot of mangakas \Ndraw their ideal girl as the heroine.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.20,0:03:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really easy to draw!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.65,0:03:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, then here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first 15 pages.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think it's alright, can I get a clean copy?
