Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.49,0:03:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The main character's an angel, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen pirates, ninjas, death gods, and spirits—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.62,0:03:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think I've ever seen an angel \Nas the main character in a Jack manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.27,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I figure if he's good looking, \Nthe girls will like him too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.88,0:04:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't there a manga \Ncalled "Flower Angel Ten-Ten?"
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was a gag manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked it as a kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.51,0:04:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That just means this one will \Ndo well with kids too, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.54,0:04:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.60,0:04:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you actually look for a series with an angel \Nas the main character, you'll find plenty.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're worried about never copying anything,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.74,0:04:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll never be able to write anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The angel kills somebody right off the bat?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an evil angel.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.64,0:04:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the angels' job to send \Nhumans who have died to heaven.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.49,0:04:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Many angels come down to Earth \Nand kill humans to gain extra points.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.37,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Our angel of justice has come \Ndown to try and prevent this.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He falls in love with a human girl
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.51,0:04:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and fights the evil angels.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.67,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll give it a moving ending.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty confident we can pull this off.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is good.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.10,0:04:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got all the things Hattori mentioned before, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.94,0:04:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.94,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a bit sudden,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.08,0:05:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but you've heard of the "Golden Future Cup," right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.78,0:05:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. You guys did that last year as well, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.88,0:05:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The one where all the \Nnewcomers submit one-shots?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're doing it again this year,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.45,0:05:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and since you did so well in Next, we'd like to know if you're interested in submitting a name for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We'll do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're actually writing something great right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think about 20 names are up for consideration,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.23,0:05:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but only four or five will actually be accepted.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the deadline is June 25th,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.69,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't have much time.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.36,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,We can make it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And with time to spare!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.98,0:05:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.99,0:05:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can get first, then getting \Nserialized won't be just a dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make this happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.67,0:05:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a name ready three days before the \Ndeadline so we still have time to make changes!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.33,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.28,0:05:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think the main character \Nshould look exactly like a human.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.93,0:05:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.04,0:05:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The readers need to be able to tell the \Ndifference between angels and humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi! Mashiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody gave me some movie tickets!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go after school?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.36,0:06:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we've gotta go turn in our manuscript.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.84,0:06:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So what should we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.79,0:06:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name, you can always see his wings.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.52,0:06:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about he has them out \Naround people who know he's an angel,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.03,0:06:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but keeps them hidden otherwise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.90,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\fs32.089\1c&HDBD3D0&\pos(480,217.269)\frz18.6\fax0.01\blur1.003\b1}Azuki Miho
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.73,0:06:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She had a lesson today.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be nice to have a dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a dream too!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.16,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You've managed to put everything I said about \Nmainstream battle mangas into the story.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.15,0:06:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And so naturally, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi is even more skilled than I thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.54,0:06:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I didn't think he'd be \Nable to write a battle manga this well.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.87,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.76,0:06:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,T—Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.57,0:06:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'm just your editor.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only give you advice.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones who are able to build \Non that and take it even further
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.28,0:06:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,are the ones who will be successful.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.94,0:07:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.98,0:07:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Editors can't write a story \Nguaranteed to be a smash hit!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could, we'd just do it ourselves!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.61,0:07:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mangakas must be better than their editor!!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you mean this name is no good?
Comment: 10,0:07:21.31,0:07:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is good how it is,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.93,0:07:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you're aiming to get better, \Nyou have to not only do what I've said,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.27,0:07:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but also be able to surprise me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro's drawings, as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They feel pretty solid, so they pass.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to go beyond my advice
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.49,0:07:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and create something original.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.36,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that nobody else could make.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.02,0:07:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be too much for a Jack-level manga,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but to make me say this much, \Nyou're already very talented.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.28,0:07:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'll submit this \Nto the "Golden Future Cup."
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.91,0:08:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a little surprised to hear Hattori \Nsay we had what it takes to write mainstream.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He got pretty excited.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be fine, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.62,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.59,0:08:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we did pretty well,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.93,0:08:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but did it have anything that really stands out?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.66,0:08:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that stands out?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll probably make it into the contest,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.97,0:08:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but it feels like we were told that the winner will \Nbe the one that surprises the editors the most.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle said something similar.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.02,0:08:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of people out there \Nwho can debut and win an award,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but the tough part comes after that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.03,0:08:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}Only a small percentage of those \Nmanage to get as far as serialization.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.40,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, now I can't even be happy \Nabout being an entry for the contest.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to win and get serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.50,0:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Popularity.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.26,0:08:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Popularity.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.29,0:08:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be popular!!!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.75,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Knock it off! You're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming by.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.43,0:08:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Shimoyama?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.56,0:08:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he quit.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.94,0:08:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.09,0:08:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Um—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.80,0:09:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can manage the drawings on my \Nown, but the atmosphere is kinda—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.86,0:09:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be great if I could get one or two more people.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.66,0:09:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking your manuscript, alright?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, when did you get here?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Ashirogi-sensei doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.29,0:09:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Oh,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.16,0:09:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,they submitted a name for \Nthe "Golden Future Cup."
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.54,0:09:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean that contest?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.10,0:09:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.92,0:09:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So they'll have another one-shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi-sensei will definitely win!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.76,0:09:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.01,0:09:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Crow!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.17,0:09:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't even get into the contest?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.47,0:09:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's too bad, but that's what they decided.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.88,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That, and—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.85,0:09:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he submitted it for \Nthis summer's Next as well,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.28,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but it didn't get accepted there, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe mainstream really is impossible for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to write a mainstream manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.61,0:09:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't write stories like you do.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go with something that you—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.28,0:10:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're aiming for the top together!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be told today of all days—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can't even enjoy Azuki's anime.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I said that,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.09,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still really nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:24.68,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,St. Visual's Girls Academy
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It started!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.98,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,We are saints!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:37.86,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,My heart starts beating anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:41.78,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,After we meet, let's ring the school bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.87,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,Your heart—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.30,0:10:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost over.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Azuki really gonna show up?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,E—Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.63,0:10:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.84,0:10:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Saotomeji!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.63,0:10:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.73,0:11:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,came to this school because you were here.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.01,0:11:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I—I love you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.81,0:11:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Erina-senpai.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"I love you?"
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.88,0:11:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.98,0:11:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this awful development?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.19,0:11:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Shuujin!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.33,0:11:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,S—Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.69,0:11:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.90,0:11:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So she only had four lines—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.04,0:11:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was better than I imagined it would be.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.38,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Azuki—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.62,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm Otsuki Nanami, the voice of Ijunin Erina
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.62,0:11:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.33,0:11:34.42,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,and we're giving away copies of the "St. Viz Girls" album to a few lucky viewers—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah! She's on TV!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.13,0:11:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that was probably embarrassing for her.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Being on TV in cosplay.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Azuki's the same as us.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd want to be right up in the front.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.22,0:11:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki's been trying her best to get this far!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.02,0:11:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just sit around and feel depressed!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.23,0:11:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.74,0:12:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Suda.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.37,0:12:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.66,0:12:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Segawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.43,0:12:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.53,0:12:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi's absent?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.79,0:12:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice weather, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your phone's ringing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.98,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it was a bit of a shock, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.44,0:12:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, well—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.95,0:12:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.28,0:12:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you disappointed?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.04,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.95,0:12:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.46,0:12:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I put your name in here and passed it around
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.05,0:12:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as a candidate for the "Golden Future Cup."
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all the comments it got.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.05,0:13:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:07.30,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)\blur0.869\move(800,480.665,209.333,480.665)}I can't believe this was written by the same \Npair that wrote "Money and Intelligence."\NHowever, the writing is too textbook. \N\N\NI don't think we should run it. Shows much promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:14.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,880)\blur0.869\move(880,501.389,10.667,501.389)\fs60.167}Shows much promise.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.19,0:13:25.53,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,890)\an7\move(1453.333,53.481,219.333,53.481)\fs46.796\blur0.869}It looks like they want to write something that will make\Nit big. They're so young, yet already sound like pros!\NI really want to see them get serialized!!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:24.61,0:13:30.83,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,0)\an7\move(1633.333,414.481,66.667,414.481)\fs46.796\blur0.869}I really want to see them get serialized!!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I—I can't—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read any more.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.96,0:13:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuujin—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.30,0:13:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori, you didn't write \Nall of this yourself, did you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do something like that.
