Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.98,ShopSign,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H6DA2F9&\frz14\fax0.3\b1\blur0.869\move(470.667,363.674,482.667,400.443,0,691)}Cellphone novel written by female\Nhigh school student becomes bestseller\N{\1c&H7178DD&}Sold over one million copies!
