Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.86,0:14:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect the editing department \Nto think we have so much promise.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was surprised too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.20,0:14:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just putting more pressure \Non me to write something great.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi sure is amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.08,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.67,0:14:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, when I got home, I looked into how many \Nother newcomers were close to getting serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There're at least 15.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much they expect of us,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.22,0:14:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we've only been in Next once.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta try harder.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They all say your drawings are pretty solid,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,so that just leaves my names.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.69,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,25-4, Class 3 wins.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finally finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.66,0:14:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What what?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You were watching me the whole time.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.79,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was just watching your \Nboobs bounce all over the place.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you always such a pervert?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a joke, I swear.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's true!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in a magazine!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Beautiful New Voice Actresses?"
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.72,0:15:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She was also on the home page of her agency.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.15,0:15:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Her high school doesn't allow you to work,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.11,0:15:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so she almost got in trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a mail that said they're going to allow it
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.48,0:15:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,because she's always a hard worker.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.74,0:15:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as she makes her studies a priority.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A serious, cute girl is poison, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.90,0:15:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.49,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,did you come here just to show us this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.65,0:15:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Announcement!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.86,0:15:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Announcement?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.11,0:15:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I have also chosen my dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.66,0:15:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.63,0:15:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to become a writer.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.58,0:15:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A writer?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.01,0:15:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho's a voice actress.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.43,0:15:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are mangakas.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.43,0:15:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to fit in with all of \Nyou, so I decided on a writer.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.72,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,What's with that shallow way of thinking?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.38,0:15:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it is only cellphone novels.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.48,0:15:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of companies \Npublishing them online.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And what're you gonna write?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.94,0:15:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A love story.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.07,0:15:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll model it after Miho and Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.52,0:16:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'll replace 'mangaka' and \N'voice actress' with 'writer' and 'actress.'
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And the part about playing \Nthe heroine in his anime
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.74,0:16:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,will be her starring in a drama he wrote.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that might be interesting!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.70,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Why are you supporting her?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.70,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you think you can help me out?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.75,0:16:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, I'll tell you how to write a \Ngood female character for your manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.66,0:16:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I do need a good \Nheroine for the story I'm writing now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! It's decided then!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.46,0:16:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that you want to have a dream too,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't want you sticking \Nyou nose into our manga!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.85,0:16:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.54,0:16:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to understand a woman's feelings, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.77,0:16:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shounen manga,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.36,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's fine with a man's ideal girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Takagi's the one writing the story!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.85,0:16:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've already written a bit on my phone,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.78,0:16:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so could you take a look?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuujin!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.19,0:16:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all too textbook! No originality!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't uninteresting,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.97,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but they all feel like our "Golden Future Cup" entry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't change anything,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.13,0:17:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll just end up like before.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.54,0:17:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.58,0:17:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the mainstream \Nstories I write {\i1}do{\i0} all feel similar.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm trying too hard to \Ndo everything Hattori said.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.72,0:17:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try a different approach and see if that works.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Saiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm any good the way I am right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.03,0:17:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Any good?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.79,0:17:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like I'm forcing out a story every day.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Like in order to force a character to move,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking up strange, fantastic settings.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good, is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta come up with a good character.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.24,0:17:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that'll move on \Nit's own, like Eiji's characters do.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.91,0:17:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can do that, I think I can write \Nsomething better than what I've done so far.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure why I can't come up with anything,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's summer vacation,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so I think I'm going to take a break and \Ntry and think of something on my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.24,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.67,0:18:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.94,0:18:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.23,0:18:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to write an \Ninteresting name this summer.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Mashiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.92,0:18:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, with the runner-up \Nof the recent "Story King."
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro's drawings would be perfect.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't ask the impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.45,0:18:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course that wouldn't be okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.23,0:18:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi Muto is a two-man team, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.07,0:18:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I figured.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.40,0:18:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll have to try somebody else, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.36,0:18:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.99,0:19:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How about if he works as an assistant?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.17,0:19:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,An assistant?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean for Niizuma?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.21,0:19:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.37,0:19:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were an assistant working \Nfor a 16-year-old mangaka,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.05,0:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it probably wouldn't make you feel too great.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.88,0:19:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro is younger and his drawings are great.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright even if it's just for the summer.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.00,0:19:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi Muto sees Niizuma as their rival.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.77,0:19:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he'd go.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.02,0:19:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you at least ask him for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.34,0:19:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all editors, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.19,0:19:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We should help each other out.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, but only if they both agree to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.35,0:19:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they will, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.65,0:19:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.12,0:19:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time you've \Ninvited me out on a date.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Movie, karaoke, or bowling?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.93,0:19:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Bowling.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.22,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Shuujin.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.23,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He didn't come today, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.85,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He hasn't contacted me at all \Nsince the break started, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.80,0:20:08.57,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I guess writing mainstream really is tough.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.03,0:20:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you scored over 200!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you broke 100, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just going easy on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I want to go to karaoke.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.81,0:20:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.46,0:20:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my phone's ringing.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.74,0:20:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.63,0:20:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.58,0:20:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You writing?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.99,0:20:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.97,0:20:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm writing,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.89,0:20:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but nothing I'm quite satisfied with.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.08,0:20:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.30,0:20:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually called because someone is \Nasking for Mashiro to be an assistant.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.67,0:20:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,An assistant?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.34,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I should see if you were \Nokay with it before talking to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.52,0:20:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,right now I've got writer's block.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.27,0:20:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really come up with anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just making Mashiro wait
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.49,0:21:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and I feel bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.56,0:21:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So if Mashiro says he'll do it,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.92,0:21:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stop him.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.83,0:21:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.95,0:21:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, an assistant?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.59,0:21:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and it's alright if it's just for the summer.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.51,0:21:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're both aiming for \Nserialization right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.71,0:21:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I talked to Takagi about it already.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.97,0:21:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he wouldn't stop \Nyou if you decided to do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi said that?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.80,0:21:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you'd be working for Niizuma, so—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.01,0:21:32.14,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Niizuma Eiji—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.39,0:21:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make sure that your series continues
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.70,0:21:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and wait for us to get serialized as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.23,0:21:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I might already be \Nnumber one by then, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.73,0:21:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's completely up to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was actually reluctant to even ask,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but decided to just in case.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.06,0:21:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.95,0:21:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro as an assistant?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.80,0:21:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, helping out another mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.54,0:22:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he's part of Ashirogi Muto?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.09,0:22:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one making him wait, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.46,0:22:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite the fact that I'm the one who \Nasked him to write manga in the first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.14,0:22:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, we should be getting home.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.72,0:22:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.89,0:22:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I getting in the way?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.36,0:22:25.12,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,If I go to Eiji's, I should \Nbe able to learn something.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.61,0:22:27.66,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It'll benefit Shuujin as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.27,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always wondered "Why am I the only one having a hard time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.27,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,doushite boku dake ga kon'nani tsurai no ka to itsumo omotteta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.73,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The people around me all seemed so happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.73,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,mawari no hito bakari shiawase sou ni mieta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:08.24,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But when I talked to you, I felt just a little bit better
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:08.24,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,dakedo kimi to hanashitara sukoshi dakedakedo ki ga raku ni natta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.74,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because we were open with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.74,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,nita youna koto uchiakete kuretakara kana
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:21.25,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the reality you can't see with your eyes is like a monster
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:21.25,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,kao no mienai genjitsu ga toki ni kaibutsu no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:28.51,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our ambitions are crushed, but we move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:28.51,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,bokura no kokorozashi wo tsubusou to oshiyosete kurukeredo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:34.64,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can say from the bottom of my heart that I'm glad I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:34.64,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,deaete yokatta to kokoro kara ieru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.56,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,People are multiplying little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.56,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,hito ga sukoshi zutsu fuete ku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:41.31,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,While clenching their warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:41.31,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,sono nukumori wo kamishimenagara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:47.28,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could support each other or face the boring things head on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:47.28,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,sasae attari hikutsu wo butsuke attari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:50.49,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll finally arrive at that place alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:50.49,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,hitori ja tadori tsukenai basho ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:57.33,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}We're now proceeding en route
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:57.33,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}bokura wa ima kitto omomuite iru tochuu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:06.42,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}en route
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:06.42,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}tochuu
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.97,0:24:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Otsuki Nanami, the voice of Ijunin Erina.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:19.85,Next Ep,,0,0,0,,{\pos(80,76.88)\clip(59,78,1165,231)}Next\NEpisode
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.72,0:24:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Azuki Miho, the voice of Saotomeji Reika.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.85,0:24:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on "St. Visuals—
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.23,0:24:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong show, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:29.99,Next Ep,,0,0,0,,{\pos(120,66.852)\clip(85,64,531,215)}Conceit and \NKindness
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.11,0:24:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: Conceit and Kindness.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If your dreams are conceited, \Nthey're better off not coming true!
